description.narrative: UNICEF continues to support health technical advisory group (humanitarian), reproductive health and child health TWG (which may be expanded to wider RMNCAH), CMR TWG, EPI TWG, thematic working groups at national and sub-national levels. Most notably, UNCEF supported the MoH to develop, validate and launch the Every-New-born Action Plan, which will be costed and will inform implementation planning in 2020. These activities are expected to strengthen the quality of maternal and newborn primary health care according to the quality, equity and dignity (QED) guidelines. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:31/12/2019
